Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.50,0:24:18.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.83,0:24:20.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}要好好地看哦！
